---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout>
  <header id="hero" role="banner" class="mb-6 mt-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Dylan Bateman</h1>
    <p class="text-md text-[#439A86] mb-8" role="heading" aria-level="2">
      Software Engineer
    </p>
  </header>

  <section
    id="about-me"
    role="region"
    aria-label="About Dylan Bateman"
    class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/40 to-gray-700/20 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 mb-8"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left"
    >
      <div>
        <h2
          class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start"
        >
          Hey, I'm Dylan üëã
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
          I'm a passionate full-stack software engineer who wants to use code to
          solve real-world problems. With expertise in <b>React</b>,
          <b>TypeScript</b>, and <b>Node.js</b>. I'm inspired by innovative
          companies that revolutionise their sectors to benefit users.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img
          src="/profile.jpeg"
          alt="Dylan Bateman"
          class="max-w-32 h-auto rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-gray-700/50 shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    id="personality"
    role="region"
    aria-label="Personal Interests"
    class="mb-16"
  >
    <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
      <div class="text-sm text-[#439A86]/70 font-bold tracking-wider">
        the "me" portion
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-[#439A86]/50 to-transparent flex-grow ml-4"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div role="list" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">
      <article
        role="listitem"
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/40 to-gray-700/20 rounded-lg shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30 group overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
          <div class="md:w-2/5 relative">
            <img
              src="/resources/football_1.jpeg"
              alt="American football action shot"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              style="min-height: 240px;"
            />
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-[#02242e] opacity-40 md:block hidden"
            >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-3/5 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full text-[#439A86] flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-xl"
              >
                üèà
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">
                American Football
              </h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Outside of coding, a big part of my life is playing American
              Football with the Shropshire Revolution. It's a fantastic team
              sport that I found during my time at Uni - and I'm really glad I
              did!
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Being part of the Revolution has taught me valuable lessons that
              extend beyond the field. Understanding the importance of
              individual roles but also how they work within the wider team,
              adapting to changing situations, and clear communication are all
              key aspects of success in football ‚Äì and surprisingly relevant to
              how I collaborate and approach problem-solving in software
              development.
            </p>
            <div
              class="pt-2 border-t border-gray-700/30 mt-4 flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-400"
            >
              <span>Since 2023</span>
              <a
                href="https://shropshirerevolution.com"
                class="text-[#7950cc] hover:text-white transition-colors font-medium"
              >
                Shropshire Revolution
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article
        role="listitem"
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/40 to-gray-700/20 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">
              ‚öΩ Football & F1 üèéÔ∏è
            </h3>

            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              I've been a Wolves season ticket holder since I was a kid and have
              experienced the ups and downs of following the club. Despite the
              (more than) occasional frustrations, I love football and going
              home to Molineux.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Away from a pitch, I'm also a Formula 1 fan. It really grabbed me
              a few years ago and the high intensity and the different
              strategies interests me. I'm hoping to finally tick attending a
              Grand Prix off my bucket list this year!
            </p>
            <div
              class="pt-2 border-t border-gray-700/30 mt-4 flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-400"
            >
              <span class="text-[#FDB913]">Wolverhampton Wanderers</span>
              <span class="text-[#FDB913]">McLaren</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article
        role="listitem"
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/40 to-gray-700/20 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">
              üéÆ Video Games
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Video games have been a constant in my life efrom early childhood.
              That early passion for playing eventually evolved into a curiosity
              about how they were made. It was through this interest with my
              brother, that I first discovered the world of programming. This
              ultimately led me to pursue a degree in Games Development, which
              was a fantastic journey in understanding the technical side of
              creating interactive experiences.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section role="region" aria-label="Work Philosophy" class="mb-16">
    <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
      <div class="text-sm text-[#439A86]/70 font-bold tracking-wider">
        ...enough about me
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-[#439A86]/50 to-transparent flex-grow ml-4"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/40 to-gray-700/20 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30"
    >
      <div role="list" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <article role="listitem">
          <div class="mb-4 text-[#439A86] text-2xl font-bold">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Team Vibes</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Honestly, I love working in a collaborative team. Bouncing ideas off
            each other, having open conversations, and coming up with solutions
            together.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article role="listitem">
          <div class="mb-4 text-[#439A86] text-2xl font-bold">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
            Continuous Learning & Adaptability
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Tech is constantly evolving, and I enjoy learning new technologies
            and methodologies to deliver the best results
          </p>
        </article>
        <article role="listitem">
          <div class="mb-4 text-[#439A86] text-2xl font-bold">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
            Making Things People Actually Want to Use
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Creating software that makes a positive difference in people's lives
            is what truly motivates me!
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section role="region" aria-label="Contact Information" class="mb-16">
    <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
      <div class="text-sm text-[#439A86]/70 font-bold tracking-wider">
        contact me
      </div>
      <div
        class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-[#439A86]/50 to-transparent flex-grow ml-4"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/40 to-gray-700/20 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700/30"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Get in Touch!</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If you have an exciting project in mind or would like to explore how my
        skills can contribute to your team, I'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a
          href="mailto:dylan@dylanbateman.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700/50 hover:bg-[#439A86] text-white hover:text-[#02242e] rounded-md font-bold text-sm transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <span>Email</span>
          <svg
            width="15"
            height="15"
            viewBox="0 0 15 15"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="size-5"
          >
            <path
              d="M1.5 3.5C1.5 2.94772 1.94772 2.5 2.5 2.5H12.5C13.0523 2.5 13.5 2.94772 13.5 3.5V11.5C13.5 12.0523 13.0523 12.5 12.5 12.5H2.5C1.94772 12.5 1.5 12.0523 1.5 11.5V3.5ZM3.01944 3.5L7.5 7.01099L11.9806 3.5H3.01944ZM12.5 4.51944L7.7942 8.4084C7.59398 8.57025 7.30602 8.57025 7.1058 8.4084L2.5 4.51944V11.5H12.5V4.51944Z"
              fill="currentColor"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/dylanbateman"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700/50 hover:bg-[#439A86] text-white hover:text-[#02242e] rounded-md font-bold text-sm transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <span>GitHub</span>
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            ><path
              d="M12 0C5.374 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23A11.509 11.509 0 0112 5.803c1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576C20.566 21.797 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://linkedin.com/in/dylanbateman"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700/50 hover:bg-[#439A86] text-white hover:text-[#02242e] rounded-md font-bold text-sm transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <span>LinkedIn</span>
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            ><path
              d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/dylanbateman_"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-700/50 hover:bg-[#439A86] text-white hover:text-[#02242e] rounded-md font-bold text-sm transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <span>Twitter</span>
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            ><path
              d="M23.953 4.57a10 10 0 01-2.825.775 4.958 4.958 0 002.163-2.723c-.951.555-2.005.959-3.127 1.184a4.92 4.92 0 00-8.384 4.482C7.69 8.095 4.067 6.13 1.64 3.162a4.822 4.822 0 00-.666 2.475c0 1.71.87 3.213 2.188 4.096a4.904 4.904 0 01-2.228-.616v.06a4.923 4.923 0 003.946 4.827 4.996 4.996 0 01-2.212.085 4.936 4.936 0 004.604 3.417 9.867 9.867 0 01-6.102 2.105c-.39 0-.779-.023-1.17-.067a13.995 13.995 0 007.557 2.209c9.053 0 13.998-7.496 13.998-13.985 0-.21 0-.42-.015-.63A9.935 9.935 0 0024 4.59z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
